reviewText: I thought this was traditional wrestling. I should have read thoroughly. It was comical, got a one minute laugh before I had to turn it off. I had hopes that it would be a good tool to share the gospel with high school wrestlers, but it would not.
Fascinating!  Explores a culture in America that few would even imagine exists, and does so in an intelligent and sensitive manner.  Truly shows how unique and wondrous a country we live in!
